long_description \
                    Shapely is a Python package for manipulation and \
                    analysis of 2D geospatial geometries. It is based on \
                    GEOS (http://geos.refractions.net). Shapely 1.0 is not \
                    concerned with data formats or coordinate reference \
                    systems.

